'''The 7th Saga''' (known as '''Elnard''' in Japan) is a notoriously difficult RPG featuring seven selectable protagonists competing to gather seven runes.

==Overview==

Notable features:
* Seven playable characters with unique stories
* AI rivals that level up with you
* High difficulty (US version significantly harder)
* Mode 7 world map
* Crystal Ball radar system

