==Rival System==

* Other apprentices compete for runes
* They level up as you do
* Can be allies or enemies
* Some may be fought as bosses
* Party of up to 2 characters

==Version Differences==

The US version has significant changes:
* Enemy stats dramatically increased
* Experience gains reduced
* Player stats reduced from JP version
* Generally considered much harder

